fulltitle: Contra Drug Running: Testimony of Gary Betzner and Contra Leaders (Apr  7, 1988)
title: Contra Drug Running: Testimony of Gary Betzner and Contra Leaders (Apr  7, 1988)
_filename: _Contra Drug Running - Testimony of Gary Betzner and Contra Leaders (Apr  7, 1988).webm
description:
APRIL 7, 1988 | The subcommittee hears testimony on methods of drug smuggling from convicted drug smuggler Gary Betzner and the videotaped testimony of the ARDE (Southern Front Contras) leaders.

This video has had two fifteen minute recesses removed.

Original: https://www.c-span.org/video/?2124-1/drug-control-central-america-day-4

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
